even say I would win

04:50.551 --> 04:51.595
Mother of the Year award.

04:53.467 --> 04:54.990
Not because of my own kids,

04:55.077 --> 04:58.515
but because of my life's
passion at my activity center.

04:58.602 --> 04:59.995
I work with kids.

05:00.082 --> 05:02.389
I love them with all
my heart and soul,

05:02.476 --> 05:05.435
and in return,
they love me back.

05:05.522 --> 05:09.178
They give my life a
sense of significance.

05:10.919 --> 05:14.183
I'll be honest, things
haven't been easy lately,

05:15.576 --> 05:17.491
but no matter how
bad things get,

05:18.579 --> 05:20.363
when I look at their faces

05:20.450 --> 05:24.454
and I see the hope in
their eyes, who knows?

05:24.541 --> 05:27.631
Maybe God has some sort of
divine intervention for me.

05:29.198 --> 05:30.808
Maybe it's right
around the corner.

05:37.337 --> 05:39.469
