07:00.115 --> 07:01.464
yours has a little extra
something something,

07:01.551 --> 07:02.596
mine, nothing.

07:03.684 --> 07:04.946
- Rox, you're ridiculous.

07:05.033 --> 07:06.600
A guy hasn't looked
at me since--

07:06.687 --> 07:10.168
- Oh, no, do not bring up the
Max this and the Max that.

07:10.255 --> 07:11.735
He went off to New
York, or wherever,

07:11.822 --> 07:12.823
and it's been what?

07:12.910 --> 07:13.955
Two years?

07:14.042 --> 07:16.653
Two very long and lonely years.

07:16.740 --> 07:18.699
Time to plant a
new garden, honey.

07:18.786 --> 07:21.223
I say start with
some Italian herbs.

07:21.310 --> 07:24.313
