good look into the kitchen,

07:31.233 --> 07:32.495
how 'bout you tell me

07:32.582 --> 07:33.931
when the Italian
stallion comes into view.

07:34.889 --> 07:36.368
- I am ignoring you.

07:36.456 --> 07:39.110
- Yeah, well, you
could try to do that.

07:39.937 --> 07:40.982
- Hi.

07:41.069 --> 07:41.939
- Good afternoon, ladies.
- Hi.

07:42.026 --> 07:43.375
- Welcome to the Peppermill.

07:43.463 --> 07:44.942
Can I start y'all off
with something to drink?

07:45.029 --> 07:46.944
- I would like a water
with no lemon, please.

07:47.031 --> 07:48.555
- Okay.

07:48.642 --> 07:52.080
- Oh, and a vodka martini,
dirty, with three olives.

07:53.298 --> 07:54.386
- Okay.
- Well, you know,

07:54.474 --> 07:55.387
make it a double.
- Okay.

07:55.475 --> 07:56.606
- Yeah.

07:56.693 --> 07:58.956
What?
- Are you done yet?

07:59.043 --> 08:00.567
- It's five o'clock somewhere.

08:01.437 --> 08:02.743
- And for you?

08:02.830 --> 08:04.658
- I'll just have a
water, thank you.

08:04.745 --> 08:05.441
- Water?

08:06.398 --> 08:07.704
- What's wrong with water?

08:07.791 --> 08:08.836
It's good for you.

08:12.492 --> 08:13.188
What?

08:13.275 --> 08:14.668
What now?

08:14.755 --> 08:15.930
- I don't know, I
was just wondering

08:16.017 --> 08:17.671
about what maybe you had planned

08:17.758 --> 08:21.675
for say the first
week of the summer?

08:21.762 --> 08:23.328
- Why, pray tell,
are you asking?

08:24.721 --> 08:26.723
- Because I have
this vision of you

08:26.810 --> 08:29.639
with your cute
little recyclable bag

08:29.726 --> 08:31.249
heading into the used bookstore

08:31.336 --> 08:34.688
and filling it up with
$2 romance novels,

08:34.775 --> 08:36.558
and then sitting home on
Friday and Saturday night

08:36.645 --> 08:38.735
after you get back from
the gym to read them.

08:40.171 --> 08:42.652
You, my girl, are
predictable and boring.

08:44.306 --> 08:45.655
I love you, I do,

08:47.439 --> 08:49.833
but you have got to get a little
fun in your life, capeesh?

08:50.834 --> 08:52.749
- Oh my god, it's him.

08:52.836 --> 08:55.012
- What?
- It's him.

08:55.099 --> 08:57.101
- Yeah, it is.
- Don't look at him.

08:57.188 --> 08:57.972
- What?

08:58.059 --> 08:59.451
Ow, that hurt.

08:59.539 --> 09:01.236
- Don't, stop.
- Why not?

09:01.323 --> 09:04.108
Look at him, he is like
one of those statues

09:04.195 --> 09:07.024
in a fountain that you're
supposed to look at.

09:07.111 --> 09:08.852
He's beautiful.
- You're crazy.

09:08.939 --> 09:09.592
- Come on.

09:10.637 --> 09:12.290
Just look at him, seriously.

09:12.377 --> 09:13.683
Just take a look.

09:13.770 --> 09:15.772
Take a look.
- Crazy woman.

09:15.859 --> 09:16.643
- [Roxanne] I am.

09:18.819 --> 09:21.212
[boys chattering]

09:21.299 --> 09:22.344
- Justin, go long.

09:25.173 --> 09:28.306
- I just think Christian and I
would be so perfect together.

09:29.481 --> 09:30.787
- I'm sure you do.

09:30.874 --> 09:33.268
- He just has the best smile.

09:33.355 --> 09:35.313
And his eyes, don't you think?
- Yeah.

09:35.400 --> 09:37.185
- Snap out of it, girl.

09:37.272 --> 09:38.665
- He is pretty dreamy, isn't he?

09:38.752 --> 09:41.668
- [clapping] Guys, it's summer.

09:41.755 --> 09:43.713
We need to make a plan.

09:43.800 --> 09:45.497
- I plan on watching every movie

09:45.585 --> 09:46.716
that hits theaters this summer.

09:46.803 --> 09:48.370
Yes, every single one.

09:48.457 --> 09:50.067
- Oh, okay.

09:50.154 --> 09:52.592
Well, I plan on starring in
my community's summer musical.

09:52.679 --> 09:54.245
- Well, I plan on
getting discovered,

09:54.332 --> 09:57.727
and when I do, I'm
heading out to Hollywood.

09:57.814 --> 09:59.163
- [scoffs] Discovered?

09:59.250 --> 10:00.600
I don't see any Hollywood agents

10:00.687 --> 10:02.906
