door, Michael Buble.

10:02.993 --> 10:04.560
- And if they did
come to New Orleans,

10:04.647 --> 10:06.475
they'd be looking for me.

10:06.562 --> 10:07.345
- Oh, or me.

10:09.304 --> 10:10.305
- This conversation is stupid.

10:11.872 --> 10:14.135
- Well, the music I'm
gonna make with this

10:14.222 --> 10:15.876
and the Grammys I'm gonna win,

10:15.963 --> 10:17.965
