a game of foosball.

10:39.726 --> 10:42.076
- Okay, I gotta be in on this.

10:43.251 --> 10:43.947
- Count me in.

10:45.427 --> 10:46.080
- Hey, guys.

10:46.167 --> 10:46.950
How y'all doing?

10:47.037 --> 10:47.734
- [Students] Hey, Ms. A.

10:49.344 --> 10:50.693
- How was school today?

10:50.780 --> 10:53.435
- Ms. A, school's
over, it's summer now.

10:53.522 --> 10:55.393
- Yeah, thank goodness.

10:55.480 --> 10:56.699
- Wow, time flies.

10:56.786 --> 10:58.658
Summer already?

10:58.745 --> 11:00.137
Okay, we're gonna
have to talk about

11:00.224 --> 11:02.400
posting new times for the
center to be open, guys.

11:02.487 --> 11:04.838
My work hours may
be changing soon.

11:04.925 --> 11:06.230
- More patients
than usual, Ms. A?

11:07.710 --> 11:10.452
- No, the opposite
actually, but yeah,

11:10.539 --> 11:13.716
a bunch of new hopeless
romantics, just like you guys.

11:13.803 --> 11:15.979
- I mean, you gotta
love us, Ms. A.

11:16.066 --> 11:18.634
- Oh, I do, Aldrich, that I do.

11:18.721 --> 11:20.201
Well, I've got some paperwork,

11:20.288 --> 11:22.725
