and behave yourselves.

11:22.812 --> 11:26.207
[upbeat cheerful music]

11:27.338 --> 11:30.515
[students chattering]

11:31.865 --> 11:32.648
- Yeah.

11:32.735 --> 11:33.736
- No!

11:36.957 --> 11:38.959
[cheering]

11:40.874 --> 11:42.571
- We did something!

12:08.858 --> 12:10.947
- Do you ever stop
looking at yourself?

12:11.034 --> 12:13.733
- And what's wrong with
liking the way I look?

12:13.820 --> 12:16.126
- Just seems a little
self-absorbed, is all.

12:16.213 --> 12:18.781
- Well, if you cared about
your appearance at all.

12:18.868 --> 12:19.913
[laughing]

12:20.000 --> 12:21.436
- You guys, that
was really mean.

12:21.523 --> 12:22.872
- Yeah, not okay.

12:22.959 --> 12:25.353
- You know what, Lexi,
not everyone is obsessed

12:25.440 --> 12:26.876
with their appearance
like you are.

12:26.963 --> 12:27.964
- You're one to talk.

12:28.051 --> 12:29.618
Little miss perfect Parker

12:29.705 --> 12:32.055
