to lose at least five pounds.

12:42.979 --> 12:46.591
- Hmm, more like seven.
[girls laughing]

12:46.678 --> 12:48.593
- Guys, please stop fighting.

12:48.680 --> 12:49.507
- It's okay, honey.

12:49.594 --> 12:50.900
- Knock it off, okay?

12:50.987 --> 12:53.860
You're all beautiful,
end of story.

12:53.947 --> 12:55.949
- Yeah, if this is
a beauty contest

12:56.036 --> 12:57.777
I wouldn't know who to choose.

12:57.864 --> 12:59.039
Y'all are all drop
dead gorgeous.

12:59.126 --> 12:59.953
- Oh, give me a break.

13:00.040 --> 13:01.345
This is all pathetic.

13:01.432 --> 13:02.825
Stop trying to make
her feel better.

13:02.912 --> 13:04.609
- What do you think
you're doing, Abigail?

13:04.696 --> 13:05.959
You know that Belle
gets triggered

13:06.046 --> 13:07.221
with conflicts and
fights like this.

13:07.308 --> 13:08.222
- Well you know what?
- What?

13:08.309 --> 13:09.571
- She's gonna have to grow up

13:09.658 --> 13:11.051
and face the real world
one of these days.

13:11.138 --> 13:14.794
- Look, this is supposed
to be a safe place,

13:14.881 --> 13:16.926
not a place where Belle
has to face more trauma

13:17.013 --> 13:18.406
and get attacked by
bullies like you.

13:18.493 --> 13:19.929
- Oh, shut up!

13:20.016 --> 13:20.930
- Hey, no you ain't gonna
talk to her like that.

13:21.017 --> 13:24.542
[girls screaming]

13:24.629 --> 13:25.935
