15:30.451 --> 15:31.713
♪ Stop just think ♪

15:31.800 --> 15:32.670
♪ 'Cause this life
is temporary ♪

15:32.757 --> 15:34.324
♪ Could be done in a blink ♪

15:34.411 --> 15:36.065
♪ Must we judge on race,
class, and social case ♪

15:36.152 --> 15:37.632
